{"title":"枪膛里，压好子弹！","authors":["周纲"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":6,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪膛里，压好子弹！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周纲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪膛里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压着复仇的子弹，士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兵的心拉满战斗的弦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰头望长空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里云天明灿灿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩霞有多美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天有多蓝……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又怎能忘记过去啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饥寒交迫的童年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地和母亲一同呻吟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅雨似爷爷的泪泉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又怎能不想起海的那边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阴森森一座阎王殿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石的屠刀滴着鲜血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华尔街的军舰淌着毒涎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"士兵的胸膛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被愤怒填满，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发烫的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握紧着枪杆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人胆敢窜犯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"子弹啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睁开双眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把敌人消灭在面前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仇要报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨要雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血债要还！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}